Package org.apache.drill.exec.record

Class RecordValueAccessor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.drill.exec.record.RecordValueAccessor
public class RecordValueAccessor extends Object
Wrapper around VectorAccessible to iterate over the records and fetch fields within a record.
